column1: IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_l7b_estradiol_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_cortisol_d is MF 2 AND ccr_cortisone_d is MF 2 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_llb_oh_andro_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_cortisol_d is MF 1 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
